response.overview: Only the Air Force's top guns become part of the elite group of men and women who pilot F-16 Falcon Thunderbirds. Watch these combat fighter jets battle extreme g-forces as they perform challenging aerobatic moves (there's no margin for error!), such as inversions, steep climbs and rolls. The video features a stirring soundtrack by Howard Leese and a special full-length version of "Freedom," performed by Paul Shortino's The Cutt.
response.title: Thunderbirds: Skies of Thunder
